::Magmatron::

    He decided to make an appearance. He knew that only CyberShark and 
Bobertron knew of his return, so it was time for the rest to know. He went 
into the bridge and saw Shredder.
    "Good, maybe the Maximals are becoming a power now," Magmatron said to 
Shredder. He knew that Shredder might not reconize him in his new body.
